                        <div class="icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-mobile shadow"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h2> NowPark.me</h2>
                        <p>
                            Enter where you want to go. We help you <b>find the nearest available parking spot</b>. And when you get there, you don't need to bother sending SMS and solving the puzzle: what parking zone it is. We do it all for you!
                            Bonus: we remind you when your parking ticket is about to end.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 wp2 delay-05s">
                        <h2>Do you have a parking spot to offer?</h2>
                        <div class="icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-home shadow"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h2>Park in my yard</h2>
                        <p>
                            Do you have a free parking spot in your yard or garage anytime during the week? What if you <b>could rent your parking spot and earn money for that</b>? Offer your spot. Enter your address, and availability. We will connect you with drivers who want to park in your yard! Win-win, right?
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 wp2 delay-1s">
                        <h2>Do you wanna be the next parking hero?</h2>
                        <div class="icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-heart shadow"></i>
                        </div>
