                        <p>
                            Imagine, you are walking down the street and you notice a free parking spot. Why don't you <b>tag that spot on the map and be someone's parking hero</b>? Once a lucky driver parks at the spot you suggested, you earn points! If you are going enough, you will get special value.
                        </p>
